<style>
.features { padding:80px 0;background:var(--brand-light); }
.ft-title { text-align:center;font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-size:30px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:48px;letter-spacing:-.5px;color:var(--brand-dark); }
.ft-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px; }
.ft-card { background:var(--brand-white);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:36px 28px;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.06);transition:box-shadow .3s; }
.ft-card:hover { box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(31,105,240,.12); }
.ft-icon { margin-bottom:16px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; }
.ft-icon svg { width:44px; height:44px; }
.ft-card h3 { font-size:16px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--brand-dark); }
.ft-card p { font-size:14px;color:var(--brand-gray);line-height:1.5; }
@media (max-width:768px) { .ft-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; } }
</style>

<section class="features">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="ft-title">Why VertiKnee™</h2>
    <div class="ft-grid">

      <div class="ft-card">
        <div class="ft-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="#1F69F0" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="24" cy="16" r="8"/>
          <path d="M24 24v16"/>
          <path d="M16 30l8-6 8 6"/>
          <path d="M10 40l14-4 14 4"/>
          <circle cx="24" cy="16" r="2" fill="#1F69F0" stroke="none"/>
        </svg></div>
        <h3>3D Anatomic Compression</h3>
        <p>Targets the patellar tendon with precision — reduces the exact impact that causes downhill knee pain.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ft-card">
        <div class="ft-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="#1F69F0" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M8 32 Q16 20 24 20 Q32 20 40 32"/>
          <path d="M8 36 Q16 24 24 24 Q32 24 40 36"/>
          <path d="M14 38h20"/>
          <path d="M24 20V12"/>
        </svg></div>
        <h3>Breathable Tech Fabric</h3>
        <p>Moisture-wicking 4-way stretch. Stays dry and comfortable after 8+ hours on the trail.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ft-card">
        <div class="ft-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="#1F69F0" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M8 26h32"/>
          <path d="M10 26V16a6 6 0 0112 0"/>
          <path d="M26 26V16a6 6 0 0112 0"/>
          <rect x="12" y="34" width="24" height="8" rx="3"/>
          <path d="M16 34v-8"/>
          <path d="M32 34v-8"/>
        </svg></div>
        <h3>Anti-Slip Silicone Grip</h3>
        <p>Inner gel strips lock the sleeve in place. Never rolls down mid-hike.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ft-card">
        <div class="ft-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="#1F69F0" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M24 6C14 6 8 16 8 20c0 4 4 6 4 10 0 4 2 8 4 10"/>
          <path d="M24 6c10 0 16 10 16 14 0 4-4 6-4 10 0 4-2 8-4 10"/>
          <path d="M24 6v36"/>
          <path d="M16 16c4-4 12-4 16 0"/>
        </svg></div>
        <h3>Ultralight 80g</h3>
        <p>You'll forget you're wearing it — until you realize you've done 15km pain-free.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ft-card">
        <div class="ft-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="#1F69F0" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <rect x="8" y="16" width="32" height="24" rx="3"/>
          <path d="M8 28h32"/>
          <path d="M20 12V8"/>
          <path d="M28 12V8"/>
          <path d="M14 8l6-4 8 4-6 4z"/>
        </svg></div>
        <h3>Packs Flat</h3>
        <p>Roll it, fold it, clip it to your pack. Zero bulk. Always trail-ready.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ft-card">
        <div class="ft-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="#1F69F0" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M24 4L6 10v12c0 12 18 22 18 22s18-10 18-22V10z"/>
          <path d="M18 24l4 4 8-8"/>
        </svg></div>
        <h3>30-Day Trail Guarantee</h3>
        <p>Take it on 3 hikes. If your knees don't feel better, full refund. No questions.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% schema %}{"name":"Features","settings":[],"presets":[{"name":"Features"}]}{% endschema %}
